---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "June 10, 2026";
---

<Layout
	title="Terms of Service - NetWorthCurve.com"
	description="NetWorthCurve.com Terms of Service. Read our terms and conditions for using our privacy-first financial planning tools."
>
	<article class="page-article">
		<div class="page-hero">
			<div class="page-hero-content">
				<span class="page-label">LEGAL</span>
				<h1 class="page-title">Terms of Service</h1>
				<p class="page-lead">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="page-content">
			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
				<p>By accessing and using <strong>NetWorthCurve.com (the "Website")</strong>, you accept and agree to be bound by these <strong>Terms of Service ("Terms")</strong>. If you do not agree to these Terms, you may not access or use the Website.</p>
				<p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Your continued use of the Website following any changes indicates your acceptance of the modified Terms. Please review these Terms periodically for updates.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
				<p>NetWorthCurve.com provides free, web-based financial calculation tools including:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li><strong>Net worth calculator (balance sheet generator)</strong></li>
					<li><strong>Compound interest and wealth projection calculator</strong></li>
					<li><strong>Multi-currency financial modeling</strong></li>
					<li><strong>Educational content about wealth management</strong></li>
				</ul>
				<p><strong>All calculations are performed client-side within your web browser. We do not provide financial advice, investment recommendations, or professional financial services.</strong></p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>3. Disclaimer of Financial Advice</h2>
				<div class="warning-box">
					<div class="warning-icon">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
							<line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/>
							<line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Important Disclaimer</h3>
						<p>The tools and content provided by NetWorthCurve.com are for <strong>educational and informational purposes only</strong>. They are not intended as, and should not be relied upon as, financial, investment, tax, or legal advice.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p>Specifically:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Projections are hypothetical scenarios based on user inputs and do not account for all real-world variables.</li>
					<li>Past performance does not guarantee future results.</li>
					<li>All investments carry risk of loss, including potential loss of principal.</li>
					<li>Inflation, taxes, fees, and market volatility may significantly impact actual returns.</li>
					<li>Individual financial circumstances vary, and general tools may not apply to your specific situation.</li>
				</ul>
				<p><strong>You should consult with licensed financial advisors, tax professionals, and legal counsel before making any significant financial decisions.</strong></p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>4. User Responsibilities</h2>
				<p>By using this Website, you agree to:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Use the Website only for lawful purposes</li>
					<li>Not attempt to interfere with or disrupt the Website's operation</li>
					<li>Not attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
					<li>Not use automated systems to access the Website without permission</li>
					<li>Verify any calculations before relying on them</li>
					<li>Seek professional advice for financial decisions</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
				<p>The Website, including its design, text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of NetWorthCurve.com and is protected by intellectual property laws. You may:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Access and use the Website for personal, non-commercial purposes</li>
					<li>Share links to the Website</li>
					<li>Reference the Website in non-commercial educational contexts</li>
				</ul>
				<p>You may not:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Copy, reproduce, or redistribute Website content without permission</li>
					<li>Modify or create derivative works based on the Website</li>
					<li>Use the Website for commercial purposes without authorization</li>
					<li>Remove or alter any proprietary notices</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
				<p><strong>TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, NETWORTHCURVE.COM AND ITS OWNERS, OPERATORS, AFFILIATES, AND PARTNERS SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR:</strong></p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages</li>
					<li>Loss of profits, income, or data</li>
					<li>Financial losses resulting from reliance on Website calculations or content</li>
					<li>Damages resulting from errors, inaccuracies, or omissions in calculations</li>
					<li>Damages resulting from unauthorized access to your device or data</li>
					<li>Any damages arising from your use or inability to use the Website</li>
				</ul>
				<p><strong>IN NO EVENT SHALL OUR TOTAL LIABILITY EXCEED $100 USD.</strong></p>
				<p>Some jurisdictions do not allow limitations on implied warranties or exclusions of liability for consequential damages. The above limitations may not apply to you to the extent prohibited by applicable law.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
				<p><strong>THE WEBSITE AND ALL CONTENT, CALCULATIONS, AND TOOLS ARE PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, WHETHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO:</strong></p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li><strong>WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY</strong></li>
					<li><strong>FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE</strong></li>
					<li><strong>NON-INFRINGEMENT</strong></li>
					<li><strong>ACCURACY OR RELIABILITY OF CALCULATIONS</strong></li>
				</ul>
				<p>We do not warrant that the Website will be uninterrupted, error-free, secure, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>8. Third-Party Links and Advertisements</h2>
				<p>The Website may contain links to third-party websites or display third-party advertisements. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of any third-party sites or advertisers. We encourage you to review the terms and privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>9. Indemnification</h2>
				<p>You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless NetWorthCurve.com and its owners, operators, affiliates, and partners from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses (including legal fees) arising from:</p>
				<ul class="styled-list">
					<li>Your use of the Website</li>
					<li>Your violation of these Terms</li>
					<li>Your violation of any rights of another party</li>
					<li>Any financial decisions you make based on Website content</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>10. Modifications to Service</h2>
				<p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the Website at any time without notice. We shall not be liable for any modification, suspension, or discontinuation of the Website.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>11. Severability</h2>
				<p>If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary so that the remaining Terms remain in full force and effect.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>12. Entire Agreement</h2>
				<p>These Terms, together with our Privacy Policy, constitute the entire agreement between you and NetWorthCurve.com regarding use of the Website and supersede any prior agreements.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
				<p>For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
				<div class="contact-info">
					<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@networthcurve.com">contact@networthcurve.com</a></p>
					<p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/contact">networthcurve.com/contact</a></p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="summary-box">
				<h3>Summary</h3>
				<p>NetWorthCurve.com provides free financial calculation tools for educational purposes. You are responsible for verifying calculations and seeking professional advice for financial decisions. We are not liable for any financial losses resulting from use of our tools.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-article {
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.page-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--charcoal-850) 0%, var(--charcoal-950) 100%);
		padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-4);
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-hero::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 600px;
		height: 400px;
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.page-hero-content {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.page-label {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--emerald-500);
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.page-lead {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--charcoal-400);
	}

	.page-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-4);
	}

	.content-block {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
	}

	.content-block h2 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--emerald-300);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--charcoal-700);
	}

	.content-block p {
		color: var(--charcoal-200);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.styled-list {
		list-style: disc;
		padding-left: var(--space-6);
		margin: var(--space-4) 0;
	}

	.styled-list li {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
		color: var(--charcoal-200);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.styled-list strong {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.warning-box {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-4);
		padding: var(--space-5);
		background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		margin: var(--space-5) 0;
	}

	.warning-icon {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background: var(--amber-600);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.warning-icon svg {
		width: 22px;
		height: 22px;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.warning-box h3 {
		color: var(--amber-400);
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
	}

	.warning-box p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.contact-info {
		background: var(--charcoal-850);
		padding: var(--space-5);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		margin-top: var(--space-3);
	}

	.contact-info p {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
	}

	.summary-box {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--charcoal-850) 0%, var(--charcoal-800) 100%);
		border: 1px solid var(--emerald-700);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		padding: var(--space-6);
		margin-top: var(--space-10);
	}

	.summary-box h3 {
		color: var(--emerald-400);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}

	.summary-box p {
		color: var(--charcoal-300);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.warning-box {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.warning-icon {
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}

	/* Light mode */
	html.light-mode .page-hero { background: #f1f3f5; }
	html.light-mode .page-title { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .page-lead { color: #868e96; }
	html.light-mode .content-block h2 { color: #101214; border-bottom-color: #dee2e6; }
	html.light-mode .content-block p { color: #343a40; }
	html.light-mode .styled-list li { color: #343a40; }
	html.light-mode .styled-list strong { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .warning-box { background: rgba(245,158,11,.07); border-color: rgba(245,158,11,.25); }
	html.light-mode .warning-box h3 { color: #b45309; }
	html.light-mode .warning-box p { color: #343a40; }
	html.light-mode .contact-info { background: #f1f3f5; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; }
	html.light-mode .summary-box { background: #f0fdf4; border-color: #16a34a; }
	html.light-mode .summary-box h3 { color: #16a34a; }
	html.light-mode .summary-box p { color: #343a40; }
</style>
